---

<PageLayout
  title="Développement web — CPEP"
  description="Sites vitrines, refontes, SEO technique et développements spécifiques : découvrez quelques réalisations web concrètes."
  showHero={false}
>
  <section
    id="developpement-web"
    aria-labelledby="developpement-web-title"
    class="relative isolate overflow-x-clip"
  >
    <div class="mx-auto px-4 py-20 cpep-web-radial">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <!-- Intro -->
        <header class="relative z-20 max-w-4xl">

          <h1
            id="developpement-web-title"
            class="mt-6 max-w-5xl text-5xl font-bold text-text md:text-7xl"
          >
            Des sites web sobres, utiles et faits pour durer.
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-text/85">
            Sites vitrines, refontes, formulaires, galeries, SEO, tunnels de contact
            ou développements spécifiques&nbsp;: chaque projet répond à un besoin concret.
            Pas de poudre aux yeux, sauf si elle est bien optimisée.
          </p>
        </header>

        <!-- Intro secondaire -->
        <div class="mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/45 p-5 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(8,7,8,0.08)] backdrop-blur-xl">
            <Icon name="lucide:layout-template" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true" />
            <h2 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-text">Des sites clairs</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/75">
              Une structure lisible, une navigation simple et des contenus bien hiérarchisés.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/45 p-5 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(8,7,8,0.08)] backdrop-blur-xl">
            <Icon name="lucide:gauge" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true" />
            <h2 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-text">Des sites rapides</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/75">
              Performance, responsive design, SEO technique et bonnes pratiques front-end.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/45 p-5 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(8,7,8,0.08)] backdrop-blur-xl">
            <Icon name="lucide:wrench" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true" />
            <h2 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-text">Des solutions utiles</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/75">
              Formulaires, automatisations, galeries, intégrations et outils adaptés au projet.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <!-- Réalisations -->
        <section
          id="realisations-web"
          aria-labelledby="realisations-web-title"
          class="mt-24"
        >
          <div class="mb-10 max-w-3xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary">
              Réalisations
            </p>

            <h2
              id="realisations-web-title"
              class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-text md:text-5xl"
            >
              Quelques projets déjà passés en prod.
            </h2>

            <p class="mt-4 text-text/80">
              Chaque carte présente le contexte du site, le problème à résoudre
              et la solution mise en place. Simple, concret, efficace.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
            {projects.map((project) => (
              <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/45 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(8,7,8,0.08)] backdrop-blur-xl transition duration-300 hover:border-accent/50 hover:bg-white/55 hover:shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(8,7,8,0.12)]">
                <!-- Reflet liquid glass -->
                <div
                  class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl bg-linear-to-br from-white/80 via-white/20 to-primary/10 opacity-70"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                ></div>

                <!-- Ligne brillante -->
                <div
                  class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-white/90 to-transparent"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                ></div>

                <div class="relative z-10 flex h-full flex-col">
                  <div class="overflow-hidden p-3">
                    <img
                      src={project.image}
                      alt={`Aperçu du site ${project.title}`}
                      width="900"
                      height="600"
                      loading="lazy"
                      decoding="async"
                      class="aspect-[16/10] w-full rounded-xl object-cover shadow-sm transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.03]"
                    />
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col px-5 pb-5">
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
                      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-primary">
                        {project.subtitle}
                      </p>

                      <span class="rounded-full border border-primary/10 bg-white/60 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-text/60">
                        {project.label}
                      </span>
                    </div>

                    <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-text">
                      {project.title}
                    </h3>

                    <ul class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                      {project.description.map((item) => (
                        <li class="rounded-full border border-white/80 bg-white/55 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-text/70">
                          {item}
                        </li>
                      ))}
                    </ul>

                    <div class="mt-5 space-y-4">
                      <div>
                        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-accent">
                          <Icon name="lucide:circle-alert" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" />
                          Problème
                        </p>

                        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/75">
                          {project.problem}
                        </p>
                      </div>

                      <div>
                        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-primary">
                          <Icon name="lucide:check-circle-2" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" />
                          Solution
                        </p>

                        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text/75">
                          {project.solution}
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                      {project.tags.map((tag) => (
                        <span class="rounded-full border border-primary/15 bg-white/55 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-text/70">
                          {tag}
                        </span>
                      ))}
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-auto pt-6">
                        {project.lighthouse && (
                            <div class="mb-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/50 p-4 shadow-inner backdrop-blur-md">
                            <div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                                <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-primary">
                                <Icon name="lucide:gauge" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" />
                                Lighthouse
                                </p>

                                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-text/45">
                                Scores desktop
                                </span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-2">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="mx-auto grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-full border border-primary/15 bg-white/70 text-sm font-bold text-primary">
                                    {project.lighthouse.performance}
                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-1 text-[0.65rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-text/50">
                                    Perf
                                </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="mx-auto grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-full border border-primary/15 bg-white/70 text-sm font-bold text-primary">
                                    {project.lighthouse.accessibility}
                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-1 text-[0.65rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-text/50">
                                    A11y
                                </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="mx-auto grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-full border border-primary/15 bg-white/70 text-sm font-bold text-primary">
                                    {project.lighthouse.bestPractices}
                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-1 text-[0.65rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-text/50">
                                    BP
                                </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="mx-auto grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-full border border-primary/15 bg-white/70 text-sm font-bold text-primary">
                                    {project.lighthouse.seo}
                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-1 text-[0.65rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-text/50">
                                    SEO
                                </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                        )}

                        <a
                            href={project.href}
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition hover:text-accent"
                        >
                            Voir le site
                            <Icon name="lucide:arrow-up-right" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" />
                        </a>
                        </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA final -->
        <div class="relative mt-20 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/80 bg-primary p-8 text-white shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(60,110,113,0.25)] md:p-10">
          <div
            class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-white/20 via-white/5 to-transparent"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>

          <div
            class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-15"
            style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.45) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.45) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 18px 18px;"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>

          <div class="relative z-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] md:items-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/70">
                Un projet web en tête&nbsp;?
              </p>

              <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
                On part du besoin, puis on code proprement.
              </h2>

              <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-white/80">
                Site vitrine, refonte, formulaire, galerie, SEO ou outil spécifique&nbsp;:
                l’objectif est de créer quelque chose d’utile, clair et durable.
              </p>
            </div>

            <QuoteButton
              label="Parler de mon projet web"
              class="border-white/40 bg-white text-primary hover:bg-white/90"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Séparateur fin -->
        <div class="mx-auto mt-20 max-w-2xl" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-primary/30 to-primary/10"></span>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/70 bg-white/45 px-4 py-2 text-primary shadow-sm backdrop-blur-xl">
              <Icon name="lucide:layout-template" class="h-4 w-4" />
              <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-accent/70"></span>
              <Icon name="lucide:code-2" class="h-4 w-4" />
              <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-accent/70"></span>
              <Icon name="lucide:rocket" class="h-4 w-4" />
            </div>

            <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-linear-to-l from-transparent via-primary/30 to-primary/10"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>